%{{{ proc tide-dap-connected-sb { dap procs info }

A new debugging-adapter created a connection with the master ToolBus.

<<tide-dap-connected-sb>>=
proc tide-dap-connected-sb { dap procs info } {
  global Dap

  set Dap($dap,viewer) 0
  set Dap($dap,hls) {}
  set Dap($dap,file) ""
}
@

